==Abu Bakr Sadiiq==
{{Template:Infobox caliph}}
'''Abu Bakr''' '''[[Abu Bakr Sadiiq]]''' ([[ingiriis]]: Abu Bakr; [[carabi]]: أبو بكر الصديق; magaca dhamaystiran Cabdullah ibn Abi Quhafa "عبد الله بن أبي قحافة") dhashay Oktoobar 573 [[C.D]] magaalada [[Makka]] ee dhulka Carabta, isla markaana dhintey 23 Ogosto 634 C.D, waa saaxiibka koowaad ee [[Nebi Muxamed]], hogaamiyihii labaad ee [[Islam|dowlada Islaamka]], asxaabi ka mid ah [[Khaliif|Kulafo Raashidiinta]] iyo mid ka mid ah asxaabta rasuulka.<ref>"'''[[Abu Bakr Sadiiq]]'''"</ref><ref>"[[ingiriis]]: Abu Bakr; [[carabi]]: أبو بكر الصديق; magaca dhamaystiran Cabdullah ibn Abi Quhafa "عبد الله بن أبي قحافة""</ref>'''<ref name=i4u>[http://www.islam4theworld.net/sahabah/abu_bakr_r.htm], from [[islam4theworld]]</ref> 

Abu Bakr wuxuu ahaa hogaamiye sare ee maamulka [[Islaam|dowlada Islaamka]] intii uu Nebigu noolaa iyo markii uu geeriyoodayba.<ref>"hogaamiye sare ee maamulka [[Islaam|dowlada Islaamka]]"</ref> Sidoo kale wuxuu ahaa [[sodog]]a iyo saaxiibka koowaad ee [[Nebi Muxamed]] (n.n.k.h). Abu Bakr<ref>"[[sodog]]a iyo saaxiibka koowaad ee [[Nebi Muxamed]]"</ref> waxa uu hogaanka iyo talada [[Rashidiinta|Khulafada Rashiidiinta]] hayay ka soo biloow 632–634 C.D markaasi oo uu noqday hogaamihii kowaad Muslimiinta iyo [[khaliif]]yada ka dib markii Nebi Maxamed geeriyooday.<ref name="brit">[http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/2153/Abu-Bakr], from [[Encyclopædia Britannica]]</ref> 

Abu Bakr waxaa loo yaqaaney ''Al-Siddiq'' (run sheege)<ref name="Campo">Juan Eduardo Campo, "Encyclopedia of Islam", Infobase Publishing, 2009 ''[http://books.google.com/books?id=OZbyz_Hr-eIC&lpg=PP1&pg=PP1#v=onepage&q&f=false]''</ref> sababtoo ah wuxuu ahaa ninkii ugu horeeyay ee rumeeya Nebiga iyo qofkii labaad ee ugu hor rumeeyay [[diin]]ta [[Islaam]]ka, waxa ka horeeyay [[xaas]]kii Nebiga waa [[Khadiijo]].
 
===Yaraantii & Islaamidii Abu Bakr===

Wakhtigii uu yaraa Abu Bakr wuxuu ahaa nin [[ganacsade]]<ref>Abu Bakr wuxuu ahaa nin [[ganacsade]]</ref> ah kaasi oo u kala safra magaalada uu deganaa ee [[Makka]], deegaanada [[Carab]]ta iyo dhulka eey jaarka yihiin ee [[Bariga Dhexe]], asaga oo kala gooshinaya badeecad, alaab iyo [[xoolo]]. Wakhtigani Abu Bakr wuxuu helay waayo-aragnimo badan iyo macaash iyo dhaqaale aad u badan taasi oo markii dambe ka taageertay in uu sharaf, heybad iyo ixtiraam fiican ku dhex yeesho beesha Quraysh ee uu ku dhashay isla markaana ku dhex noolaa. Waxaana loo aqoonsaday hoogaamiyaha beesha isla markaana loo caleemo saaray suldaanka qabiilkiisa.<ref name="autogenerated1991">The ''[[Middle East Journal]]'' by the [[Middle East Institute]], [[Washington, D.C.]], published 1991</ref> 

Mar ka mid ah safaradiisii ganacsi asagoo ka soo noqdey dalka [[Yaman]] ayaa waxaa Abu Bakr lagu wargeliyay in wakhtigii uu maqnaa ina adeerkiis Muxamed ku dhawaaqay [[Nabi|nabinimo]].<ref>"[[Yaman]] ayaa waxaa Abu Bakr lagu wargeliyay in wakhtigii uu maqnaa ina adeerkiis Muxamed ku dhawaaqay [[Nabi|nabinimo]]"</ref> Wakhti yar ka dib, markuu u kuurgalay isla markaana fahmey Abu Bakr wuu rumeeyay diintii uu soo bandhigay [[Nebi Muxamed]], wuxuuna noqday ninkii ugu horeeyay ee qaata diinta Islamka marka laga reebo [[qoys]]k rasuulka, asaga oo shaaca ka qaaday isla mar ahaantaana soo bandhigay in uu noqday qof [[Muslim]] ah.<ref>Abu Bakr Al-Siddiq - This-is-Islam.co.uk ''[http://www.this-is-islam.co.uk/drpl/men-and-women/abu-bakr-al-siddiq]''</ref>
 
===Xidhiidhka Nebiga & Abu Bakr===
Marka laga yimaado saaxiibnimada nebiga, Abu Bakr wuxuu ahaa [[sodog]]a Nebi Muxamed. [[Sanad|Sanadkii 623 C.D]] ayaa Abu Bakr al-Sadiiq [[gabadh]]iisa [[Caisha]] u aroosiyay nebiga (wakhtigaasi oo Caisha ay jirtey 9 sano); midani waxay sii adkeeysay xidhiidhka iyo isku-xidhnaanta labadooda.<ref name="Ashraf">Shahid Ashraf, "Encyclopaedia of Holy Prophet and Companions", Anmol Publications PVT. LTD., 2004, ISBN 81-261-1940-3 ''[http://books.google.com/books?id=j6ErUIqzyKoC&lpg=PP1&pg=PP1#v=onepage&q&f=false]''</ref><ref name="Campo" />
Intii [[nebi]]gu noolaa, Abu Bakr sadiiq wuxuu ahaa saaxiibka iyo la-taliyaha kowaad ee Nebi Muxamed asagoo kala qeyb galay arimo aad u badan. 

===Hogaanka Abu Bakr===
[[File:Abubakr'sreign.png|thumb|250px|Deegaanka dowlada Islaamka wakhtigii Abu Bakr.]]

Goortii nebigu u hijroonayay magaalada [[Madina]] Abu Bakr wuxuu ahaa qofka kali ah ee rasuulka la galay safarkaasi. Wuxuuna ka garab dagaalamay Nebi Muxamed qaswado aad u badan ooy ka mid yihiin [[Dagaalkii Beder]], [[Dagaalkii Uxud]], [[Dagaalkii Dhufeysyada]],<ref>"[[Dagaalkii Beder]], [[Dagaalkii Uxud]], [[Dagaalkii Dhufeysyada]]"</ref> qabsashadii magaalada [[Makka]], [[Dagaalkii Kheybar]], [[Dagaalkii Xunayn]], go'doomintii Daa'if iyo [[Dagaalkii Tabuk]].<ref>"qabsashadii magaalada [[Makka]], [[Dagaalkii Kheybar]], [[Dagaalkii Xunayn]], go'doomintii Daa'if iyo [[Dagaalkii Tabuk]]"</ref>
Dagaaladani wuxuu Abu Bakr ku kharash gareeyay in badan oo dhaqaalihiisa ka mid ah. 

Si kastaba ha ahaatee, goortii [[Nebi Muxamed]] geeriyooday waxaa [[Rashidiinta|khulafo Raashidiintu]] si waafaqsan dardaarankii nebiga isla garteen in Abu Bakr lagu wareejiyo hogaanka iyo talada maamulka dowladii Islaamka. Wakhtigani waxaa dhacday khilaaf aad u wayn oo dad badan ayaa [[diin]]ta [[Islaam]]ka dib uga noqdey maadaama nebigii waxyigu ku soo dagayay geeriyooday. 
Abu Bakr sadiiq wuxuu hogaanka dowlada Islaamka hayay [[sanad|labo sano]] iyo xoogaa ([[27|27 bilood]]) taasi oo uu isku duba ridey maamulka dowladaasi.<ref>"Abu Bakr sadiiq wuxuu hogaanka dowlada Islaamka hayay [[sanad|labo sano]] iyo xoogaa ([[27|27 bilood]]) taasi oo uu isku duba ridey maamulka dowladaasi"</ref>

